{"2922590": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "黑暗大陸編年史：墮落精靈", "steam_appid": 2922590, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90551.poster.avif?t=1740491547\" width=500 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90551.webm?t=1740491547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90551.mp4?t=1740491547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將化身為瀕臨滅絕的女精靈，踏入充滿危險與邪惡的黑暗幻想世界中探險。 在這個充滿哥布林、半獸人和邪教徒的險惡環境裡，你必須努力求存。 你可以選擇與敵人戰鬥，也可以選擇投身黑暗勢力……一切全憑你的抉擇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富的任務系統，讓你體驗最黑暗的世界觀！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中各大陣營齊聚，受詛咒的人們、哥布林、邪教徒、異獸、獸人、觸手怪……危機四伏！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各式各樣的道具和物品：食物、料理、煉金、伐木、武器製作，甚至還有催情液等情色道具！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考驗機智的解謎系統：地牢、特殊挑戰、數值培養……等著你來探索！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>遊戲仍在開發中，請加入我們的 Discord 伺服器以獲得更多資訊。</i></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90551.poster.avif?t=1740491547\" width=500 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90551.webm?t=1740491547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922590/extras/822ced421ee1ffd52e6c213992c90